		<hr />
	</div>
</div>The only ship I've unlocked is the engi drone ship. On one of my attempts with it, a fire or something killed my human, so all I was left with was two engis to manage the ship. At one point I get boarded by a bunch of mantis things just running amok in my ship. I managed to survive by fighting in the med bay. Med bay + engi ship regen bonus = unkillable muahahaha! Oh god a fire, noooooo.<br />
