</div><br />
Don't know what to tell you there, may be a bug of some type with your install - but yes, they're fire immune.  <br />
<br />
That was how I used boarding tactics when I played through with the Bulwark (rockman ship) - if they had a medbay, firebomb it then Beam in my boarding team of rockmen right into the fire.  (if no medbay firebomb some 2 slot room, then beam my guys in there.)  The opposing crew can't put out the fire while you're fighting in the room, so the fire disables the system - Your guys pound on theirs as the fire does extra damage (unless of course they have rockmen too).<br />
<br />
<a href="http://ftl.wikia.com/wiki/Races" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">http://ftl.wikia.com/wiki/Races</a></blockquote>
